>Wall": #1
>> Could I possibly run the fuel return line to one of the top vent 
>ports on my
>> tank? #2 Would it be possible to add a T-fitting to the standard 
>fuel port
>> on the bottom of the tank? I've tried Miller Fuel Injection 
>(thanks Mark)
>> and
>> they offer a sump kit which is a little cost prohibitive at $149.
>>
